cb2ea01718ef102","tid":1048860,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"你平時就應該儲定啲新聞去駁人"},{"pid":"b641cda23047f6fd6a69345045f9935cf7204bd1","tid":1048860,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:51:36.000Z","msg":"咁不如掉垃圾，衝紅燈判死刑"},{"pid":"e12ecbcf050fad4d02238504e0d32b4d13e4c701","tid":1048860,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"因為唔犯法都會被犯法"},{"pid":"9d327e935140285394da7f2206e2e03d0767075f","tid":1048860,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:53:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e5479562f0273634414fc80029256b2a2edc887","tid":1048860,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:54:12.000Z","msg":"無錯呀 好似晚晚J咁<br />\n無犯法怕乜"},{"pid":"1bd643f425384d0db7038cb2d886e5718e1a1be5","tid":1048860,"uid":104106,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"咁我冇犯法, 點解,我要比你/政府 xx"},{"pid":"ea6dbc045efff367596d334d6b147a2b2e55457e","tid":1048860,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:56:16.000Z","msg":"欲加之罪 何患無辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fe44746e6658f62a1306bfae7537ec958e6784","tid":1048860,"uid":201374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:01:44.000Z","msg":"冇得駁，哩種人唔見棺材唔會流眼淚<br />\n<br />\n例如哩個<br />\n女藍絲丈夫被警毆求助<br />\n2015年11月24日下午，一名叫Tina Lai之女網民於「小心駕駛（討論別人駕駛態度）」facebook群組留言，表示希望網友幫手，因為她的黑人丈夫於11月18日凌晨，在元朗同益大廈對開馬路，被警察查身分證，結果遭到十幾個警員毆打，想問有沒有人拍到片。她又指無論「佢做錯咩事，都唔可以用私刑！上左手扣就唔應該打。」<br />\n<br />\n然而在一眾熱心網民討論事件期間，有網友發現該名Tina Lai女網民，原來在2014年曾經參與「反佔中行動」，屬於撐警一方的藍絲帶，曾分享多則警方毆打佔領者的新聞時，力撐警方，又曾在分享熱血時報一則報道時，留言指「着住『police』字樣既背心，仲要你小老母，係佢叫人打佢，成全佢！都係抵打一族！」<br />\n<br />\n在被網民起底後，Tina即指「一件還一件，如我老公有做，佢係抵打」，有網民留言揶揄，指「你應該相信香港警察係依法行事，無做過絕對唔會屈你老公！！！！香港警察係公正嘅！」，也有網民笑稱，真係忍唔住笑左，有今日係抵！抵！抵！其後Tina可能忍受不了網民的嘲笑，退出了該專頁。<br />\n<br />\n事件經報導後網民繼續恥笑，有網民稱：「支持警方果斷執法.....市民有異議可以向監警會投訴吖」；另外有網民感嘆報應不爽：「撐警打人既藍絲，其老公被黑警打，因果報應真係快！」"},{"pid":"bb545756b9672d5fd3756ff9a2ff8cc8fac57e49","tid":1048860,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:12:52.000Z","msg":"條法例本身就係錯"},{"pid":"aa071146cb4c41569ad2ffd6d020f49897d09d76","tid":1048860,"uid":30411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7584e8fc8290666761f116de5cb2ea01718ef102","tid":1048860,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"你平時就應該儲定啲新聞去駁人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:17:52.000Z","msg":"係我唔著，次次都無貨拎出到出黎，唔夠彈藥"},{"pid":"0b1448818a17b8398b7277c86b0df3198e2cdb6c","tid":1048860,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/112031_85534f796c1e29cdd3e8945334f948b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F112031_85534f796c1e29cdd3e8945334f948b3.jpg&h=bf0d3c92&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"882740696c75b918bda5e01d10b4cd2e9fd7a22d","tid":1048860,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:25:11.000Z","msg":"法律係人訂"},{"pid":"f7cc1d715292538ecf304f47b7f76872b6d657fb","tid":1048860,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b1448818a17b8398b7277c86b0df3198e2cdb6c","tid":1048860,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/06/112031_85534f796c1e29cdd3e8945334f948b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F06%2F112031_85534f796c1e29cdd3e8945334f948b3.jpg&h=bf0d3c92&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl